You need to give every Citizen Internet Connectivity. The best Internet. Your Internet!

You start with $1.000
Every radio tower costs $500
Every house which gets internet brings you $200
A simple internet tower has a squared range of 2 tiles in every direction

Every tower costs $200 maintenance per 10 seconds
In the same time every house pays you $75

The game is over when you have no money left or when the 5 minute game counter is over

Your goal is to bring internet to all houses!
